track.name: Thyagaraja Krithi
comments: Softness personified !! and what a range of voice in Mandra Sthayi ..

Sobhana – Pantuvarali rAgam, Rupaka Talam

Lyrics:
Sobhane |
Vadana dyuti jita soma vasudhaa maanasa kaama | 
Mada maanava gaNa bheema maam paahi Sri Rama		||Sobhane||

Janaka sutaa hrudramaNa jamadagni ja madaharaNa |
praNata gaanala varuNa paahimaam muni saraNa		||Sobhane||

vigaLita mohaapaaSa vidhukoTi samkASA |
bhagavaan sakalaadheesa paahi paapa vinaasa			||Sobhane||

vara tyagarajanuta vaarij sambhaavataata |
parama kalyaaNa yuta paahimaam Subh charita			||Sobhane||
